snippet.title: STRAY | Gameplay Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Game Producer Swann talks about the world of Stray, as well as what to expect with gameplay and characters you'll come across as a cat. Coming early 2022 to PS5, PS4, and Steam. Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1332010/?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=072921&utm_medium=directreach

Lost, alone and separated from family, a stray cat must untangle an ancient mystery to escape a long-forgotten city. 

Developed by BLUETWELVE. Published by Annapurna Interactive. 

© Annapurna Interactive, 2021
